   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Make a Shelter a Home for Latin American Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Children are the invisible victims of domestic violence. Based in London, we run the only Shelter for Latin American women and children in Europe, providing a life-saving space to flee and tailored support for families to rebuild their lives. A welcoming environment is essential for a child living in a shelter to overcome their trauma. Often they come to us destitute with nothing but the clothes they&apos;re wearing. We offer essential goods,saftey and psychological assistance to help them recover</narrative>
  </description>
